rg/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M9.29 15.88L13.17 12L9.29 8.12a.996.996 0 1 1 1.41-1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39.39 1.02 0 1.41L10.7 17.3a.996.996 0 0 1-1.41 0c-.38-.39-.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I used Moonstone for purchasing my property and again years later whilst re-mortgaging, everyone who I spoke to at Moonstone were incredibly knowledgeable and helpful. Beth Hill &amp; Jack Dodd were fantastic at their roles. I would use Moonstone in the future.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">5 STAR service always, used Moonstone Advocates for years now for all our purchases and remortgages. Rebecca has always pushed it over the line smoothly. Moonstone highly recommended.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Landlord Financing &amp; Conveyancing Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Great communication, understanding, support, Knowledge. We keep coming back as well trusted.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Landlord Financing &amp; Conveyancing Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Very prompt friendly service - Moonstone Advocates get things completed rapidly and smoothly, friendly staff.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Landlord Financing &amp; Conveyancing Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I dealt with Caithlin at Black&#x27;s regarding a property related transaction. Caithlin and her team were professional, kept me updated and ultimately we achieved a perfect outcome. So I would come back to Black&#x27;s in the future.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Landlord Financing &amp; Conveyancing Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Have had an exceptional service from Aldene at Moonstone Advocates. Efficient, on the ball, professional and I felt that it was totally under control. Would highly recommend!</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Landlord Financing &amp; Conveyancing Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Richard Baum at Moonstone is outstanding. I have worked with Richard for over 12 years on a wide range of transactions, including personal and corporate property acquisitions and disposals, both privately and through auctions. </div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Landlord Financing &amp; Conveyancing Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">We’ve recently completed a number of remortgages using Moonstone Advocates as part of a lender’s panel, and the service has been excellent throughout.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Landlord Financing &amp; Conveyancing Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I was impressed by the team at Black Solicitors LLP. Every member of staff I dealt with was pleasant and professional, demonstrating a clear commitment to helping me rather than just driving up costs.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across the Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Lauren Grey at Moonstone managed the sale of my house and she was absolutely fantastic. I cannot thank her enough for her guidance, patience and support. I would recommend her (and Moonstone) to anyone looking for a professional and smooth conveyancing service and brilliant communication. Thank you!</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Landlord Financing &amp; Conveyancing Client </div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><section class=\"section_crosslink\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"crosslink_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid crosslink_content\"><div class=\"crosslink_content-left\"><h2 class=\"heading-style-h3\">Other related services</h2></div><div class=\"w-dyn-list\"><div role=\"list\" class=\"crosslink_item-list w-dyn-items\"><div role=\"listitem\" class=\"crosslink_item w-dyn-item\"><a list-link=\"trigger\" href=\"/leasehold-enfranchisement-management\" class=\"button is-text-link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"crosslink_item-text-wrapper\"><p>Leasehold Enfranchisement &amp; Management</p></div><div list-link=\"target\" class=\"crosslink_item-icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 -960 960 960\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M676.2-445.93H188.09q-14.68 0-24.37-9.7-9.7-9.7-9.7-24.37 0-14.67 9.7-24.37 9.69-9.7 24.37-9.7H676.2L456.13-734.13q-10.2-10.2-10.33-24.03-.14-13.84 10.07-24.09 10.22-10.29 24.09-10.17 13.87.12 24.15 10.31l278 278q5.46 5.52 7.94 11.48 2.49 5.97 2.49 12.66t-2.49